246
00:18:21,910 --> 00:18:26,360
who'd say that his name is
keeping peace on various islands

247
00:18:26,700 --> 00:18:31,700
but if you ask me, he's just keeping
lightweights in fear of him

248
00:18:31,700 --> 00:18:34,630
and he thinks that he's a
hero which makes me laugh!

249
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:39,090
When Roger was alive,
Whitebeard had second billing

250
00:18:39,090 --> 00:18:42,850
