he couldn't become a King.

251
00:18:42,850 --> 00:18:48,060
That means he'll never better Roger
and he'll be a loser forever!

252
00:18:48,060 --> 00:18:51,270
That's who Whitebeard
is and that's the truth.

253
00:18:53,190 --> 00:18:55,890
He's a poor man when you think about it.

254
00:18:55,890 --> 00:18:59,340
He gathered some punks who call him Pops

255
00:18:59,340 --> 00:19:02,370
and roamed around the sea
with his fake family.

256
00:19:02,370 --> 00:19:03,450
Stop it.

257
00:19:03,450 --> 00:19:06,410
And although he reigned the sea for years,

258
00:19:06,410 --> 00:19:09,500
he couldn't become a King and gained nothing

259
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:11,860
and at the end, he was stabbed by a fool,

260
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:14,300
one of his sons who fell for my line

261
00:19:15,380 --> 00:19:17,760
and he will die to protect that son.

262
00:19:18,440 --> 00:19:21,910
Don't you think that his life is so empty?

263
00:19:28,560 --> 00:19:29,560
Stop it!

264
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:31,520
Don't do it, Ace, come back!

265
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:33,060
Ace!

266
00:19:34,390 --> 00:19:39,150
Pops gave us a place to live!

267
00:19:39,690 --> 00:19:43,350
You can't understand his greatness!

268
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:48,950
People don't deserve to live
if they can't live justly!

269
00:19:48,950 --> 00:19:52,790
Punks like you guys don't
deserve a place to live!

270
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:54,040
Stop it!

271
00:19:54,040 --> 00:19:59,590
Whitebeard will die as a loser! It's
fitting for a big fish in a little barrel!

272
00:19:59,590 --> 00:20:03,180
Whitebeard is a great pirate
who shaped this era!

273
00:20:06,850 --> 00:20:10,640
Don't make fun of the man who saved me!

274
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:12,730
Don't do it, Ace!

275
00:20:12,770 --> 00:20:15,980
The name of this era should be "Whitebeard!"

276
00:20:27,120 --> 00:20:30,780
Both Whitebeard and you
guys who call him Pops

277
00:20:30,780 --> 00:20:32,620
are the same after all--losers!

278
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:41,630
Ace has been burned!

279
00:20:47,150 --> 00:20:50,700
Are you careless because you
ate a Logia type fruit which

280
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:52,770
is the most powerful of all?

281
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:58,020
You're just fire but my
magma can even burn fire!

282
00:20:58,440 --> 00:21:02,570
My power is far stronger than yours.

283
00:21:02,570 --> 00:21:04,610
Ace!

284
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:10,490
Hey, Luffy-kun, you should not fight anymore!

285
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:15,600
Ace's Vivre Card!

286
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:22,520
Gold Roger the King of the Pirates,
Dragon--the revolutionary.

287
00:21:22,520 --> 00:21:26,810
I was amazed to hear that sons
of those two are step brothers.

288
00:21:27,550 --> 00:21:30,670
You two have bad blood in your veins.

289
00:21:30,670 --> 00:21:35,640
I don't care if the others get
away as long as I get you two!

290
00:21:36,060 --> 00:21:37,600
Watch what I do.

291
00:21:40,860 --> 00:21:42,440
Wait!

292
00:21:44,550 --> 00:21:46,030
Luffy!

293
00:22:38,260 --> 00:22:41,170
This is certainly a Vivre Card.

294
00:22:41,170 --> 00:22:43,290
But I haven't told you that this card

295
00:22:43,290 --> 00:22:46,630
also tells you how much
vital energy the owner has.

296
00:22:47,140 --> 00:22:49,930
This card belongs to someone
who you care for, right?

297
00:22:49,930 --> 00:22:52,930
Yeah, it's my brother's!

298
00:22:53,820 --> 00:22:56,520
Hold onto it, always.

299
00:22:57,000 --> 00:23:01,690
That paper will lead us to one another.

300
00:23:25,450 --> 00:23:28,710
Ace is pierced by Akainu's
fist while protecting Luffy.

301
00:23:28,710 --> 00:23:32,050
Jimbei and the Whitebeard
Pirates try to save him,

302
00:23:32,510 --> 00:23:35,960
but Ace, realizing he is about to die,

303
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:39,730
finds the voice to convey his feelings
to his friends one last time.

304
00:23:39,730 --> 00:23:41,190
On the next episode of One Piece!

305
00:23:41,190 --> 00:23:44,980
"Looking for the Answer! Fire Fist Ace
Dies on the Battlefield!"

306
00:23:44,980 --> 00:23:46,980
I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
